  <brief_title>First-in-human Study of BAY2287411 Injection, a Thorium-227 Labeled Antibody-chelator Conjugate, in Patients With Tumors Known to Express Mesothelin</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label, First-in-human, Multi-center Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics and Anti-tumor Activity of a Thorium-227 Labeled Antibody-chelator Conjugate, BAY2287411 Injection, in Patients With Solid Tumors Known to Express Mesothelin</official_title>
