    <description>The dose of Thorium-227 will start at 1.5 MBq and increase in steps of 1.0 or 1.5 MBq, with a total antibody dose within the range of 10 - 50 mg. A single dose will be administered intravenously on Day 1 of each cycle lasting 6 weeks (42 days)</description>
